47:41.792 --> 47:46.897 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DON WALKER: We know from the
parish records
that people who died of the
Plague were sent

47:46.931 --> 47:48.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
