47:53.204 --> 47:58.909 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DON WALKER: Scientists
particular want to
know, what is the relationship
between the

47:58.943 --> 48:03.748 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
