about the evolution
of such diseases in the past,
the more we

48:20.331 --> 48:22.199 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
can prepare for the future,
perhaps.

48:22.233 --> 48:26.971 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Secrets
underground that may
help us today, even as the grand
