outside, it looks like, oh,
you're covering

49:06.177 --> 49:10.014 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hillary Clinton, and it's like
the most exciting
news story of the year.

49:10.047 --> 49:16.387 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
