containers on a bus,
pretty grueling, not all that
glamorous.

49:27.364 --> 49:31.969 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I had been a foreign
correspondent based in
Tokyo with The Wall Street
Journal.

49:32.002 --> 49:36.307 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
