the U.S. and
they said, how would you like to
cover Hillary

49:36.340 --> 49:38.042 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Clinton?

49:38.075 --> 49:40.711 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
