which the
Clinton people joked with me
years later,

49:40.744 --> 49:42.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that that's OK, they didn't know
what a caucus
was either.

49:42.880 --> 49:47.418 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I saw Hillary Clinton's arc
from thinking,
oh, I'm assigned to Hillary
Clinton, I'm riding

49:47.451 --> 49:51.922 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
this to the White house, to all
of a sudden
seeing her lose to Obama and
also, when she

49:51.956 --> 49:56.994 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
