50:03.133 --> 50:07.204 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She would do this famous game
that -- the
campaign trail, and that was
rolling oranges

50:07.238 --> 50:09.006 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
down the aisle of the plane.

50:09.039 --> 50:12.943 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The press sits in the back,
would write a
question on the orange and roll
it up to the

50:12.977 --> 50:14.078 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
front of the plane.

50:14.111 --> 50:15.779 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And then she writes her answer
and rolls it
back.

50:15.813 --> 50:17.748 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
