charming to a crowd of 50,000
people, and

50:29.293 --> 50:31.695 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hillary is incredibly charming
to a crowd
of five, you know?

50:31.729 --> 50:34.298 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's been a struggle for
her current
campaign.

50:34.331 --> 50:39.403 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
